  "privacyPolicyTitle": "Privacy Policy",
  "privacyLastUpdated": "Last updated: July 2, 2026",
  "privacySection1Title": "1. General Provisions",
  "privacySection1Body": "This Privacy Policy is developed in accordance with Federal Law No. 152-FZ dated 27.07.2006 \"On Personal Data\".\n\nData controller: IE Zubkov S.S. (hereinafter — the Developer).\nApplication: \"ЛетиУмно\" (hereinafter — the Application).",
  "privacySection2Title": "2. Data We Collect",
  "privacySection2Body": "The Application may collect:\n• Search queries — routes, dates, number of passengers. Used only for searching.\n• App settings (language, theme) — stored ONLY on your device.\n\nThe Application does NOT collect: full name, address, phone, email, geolocation, bank card data, advertising identifiers.",
  "privacySection3Title": "3. Purposes of Data Processing",
  "privacySection3Body": "• Searching for flights and hotels by user request\n• Providing AI recommendations for travel planning\n• Improving the quality of the application",
  "privacySection4Title": "4. Data Storage and Protection",
  "privacySection4Body": "• All data is stored exclusively on the user's device.\n• Search queries are transmitted over an encrypted channel (HTTPS/TLS).\n• The Developer does not have access to the user's local data.",
  "privacySection5Title": "5. Data Sharing with Third Parties",
  "privacySection5Body": "Search queries are transmitted to partner services (Travelpayouts) for searching flights and hotels.\n• Data is not stored on third-party servers after processing.\n• The Developer does not sell or share user data with third parties.",
  "privacySection6Title": "6. User Rights (Art. 14 No. 152-FZ)",
  "privacySection6Body": "In accordance with Federal Law No. 152-FZ you have the right to:\n• Obtain information about the processing of your data\n• Request deletion of your data\n• Withdraw consent to data processing\n\nTo delete all data, simply uninstall the application.",
  "privacySection7Title": "7. Cookies and Analytics",
  "privacySection7Body": "The Application does not use cookies or advertising trackers. The Application does not require registration.",
  "privacySection8Title": "8. Age Restrictions",
  "privacySection8Body": "The Application is intended for persons aged 12 and older.",
  "privacySection9Title": "9. Policy Changes",
  "privacySection9Body": "The Developer reserves the right to update this Policy. The current version is always available in the application.",
  "privacySection10Title": "10. Contact",
  "privacySection10Body": "For questions about data processing: zubcoder.app@yandex.ru",

